  "description": [
    "200 per year MARKET Changed every Thursday Hogs 1620 Wheat No 1 200 Corn 140 145 Oats 75 Butter 30c to Eggs 26c Cream 40c Joseph Turek of Dead wood ar rived here last Thursday afternoon for a short visit Joe came in on a dray wagon from the depot and soon was shaking hands with his many friends While here he po lished up his old EMF and trad ed it for the Buick car with John Cap He will make the trip tc Dead wood in the car He inform ed us that the mine is getting a long nicely and he and his family like their new home Vac Vlcek left for Omaha last Friday to bid farewell to his pa rents and other relatives before leaving for Camp Lewis Wash He returned Wednesday to wait for his call here B R Niki and his wife left Monday for Rochester Minn for treatment Both have not been feeling well for some time Decoration Day will be observed at Tyndall as usual The Bohe mian element will form a process ion at the ZCBJ hall at 1 oclock pm and march to the ce metery J 4 mile"
